data.description: Beautiful home located on a private cul-de-sac. Features include a large kitchen with granite countertops and a gas stove, a laundry room with utility sink, a large pantry with wood shelving and 4 spacious bedrooms. The main bedroom has a walk in closet, there are double vanities in both baths, 2 dining spaces and more! The house furnace is a Trane. The huge back yard offers a covered patio, in ground sprinklers, a  24' x 40' workshop with an additional 576 sq ft storage along the back and one side, with a 100,000 BTU Trane gas heater, overhead door, 220v and is plumbed to add a bathroom. There is even a separate 12x12 garden shed on a cement pad and RV/trailer parking.  New solid metal fence panels surround the property. A new architectural shingled roof has been installed and new windows have been ordered and will be installed soon. Six windows have already been replaced.
